headline: C3 AI Announces Fiscal Second Quarter 2026 Results
summary: REDWOOD CITY, Calif., December 03, 2025--C3.ai, Inc. ("C3 AI," "C3," or the "Company") (NYSE: AI), the Enterprise AI application software company, today announced financial results for its fiscal second quarter ended October 31, 2025.
